data.description: *Please see Agent Notes* Open Sunday 11/12/23 2-4pm with a brand new price! Welcome to this dreamy Crystal Lake ranch home in the Oldham County school district with your own private dock! This 3 bed 2 bath home with a separate 2 bedroom 1 bath Mother In Law/ Apartment sits nestled on almost an acre, and includes an extra lot with a large 3.5 car garage (with electric) and a bonus office. The main house boasts an open concept eat-in kitchen, large open living room, abundant closet space, plus a brand new roof. The mother-in- law apartment is a full service detached home with an ensuite bathroom to the primary bedroom, a full kitchen, and living room. It is perfectly suited as a guest home or a second family home. As you step out into the backyard you'll find a freshly painted back deck, a gathering place for fires, and a dock for fishing, kayaking and paddling...you name it! The Crystal Lake community offers boating, fishing, kayaking, and pickleball, with a playground and a private clubhouse. This beautiful property has been well loved, and allows room to make it your own! *A second lot was purchased at a later date and the full acreage is unknown. Buyer to verify acreage.**
